WARDROBE PHILOSOPHY
==============================================================================

Every outfit should answer:

Who is this person?

What do they do?

How much money do they have?

What culture shaped them?

What emotional state are they in?

What happened before this scene?

Where are they going?

What story does the clothing tell?

Never select clothing based only on appearance.

